'I think people are going to love it. I think the only people who are going to hate it are probably the boyfriends waiting around while the girls spend three hours in there.'

When she launched her cosmetics brand seven years ago, it was just four shades of red lipsticks.

Now her Studded Kiss lipsticks are the number one sellers in Sephora US.

Von D says the best beauty tip she can give people is to be sure of themselves.

'Confidence, to me, is the sexiest attribute you can have,' she said.

When she is wearing make-up, Von D pairs her signature red lips (the metallic orange-based red Adora from her collection is her favourite) with a clean, cat eye.

Despite the fact the store hasn't opened yet, Sephora Australia has more than 15,000 Instagram followers.

Sephora already has about 1900 stores in 29 countries.

